[size=6]Map Lock[/size]

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/kingdomcomedeliverance2/mods/831][img]https://img.shields.io/badge/Mod-Map%20Lock%20-bf4848?style=flat-square&logo=nexusmods[/img][/url] [url=https://github.com/rdok/kcd2_map_lock][img]https://img.shields.io/badge/Open-Source-2ea44f?style=flat-square&logo=github[/img][/url]


This mod saves your map spot when you close it, so it reopens right where you left off. There's a game bug, though: it only saves if you zoom or add a checkpoint. Just drop a checkpoint at your spot (it saves the map view, not the checkpoint). Install with Vortex. Drop feedback in the comments!

